    Number of (human) players - 1,2,3
    Skill Level (1,2,3)
        If 1 or 2 Players
            Vs the Computer ? (yes, no)
    
    Human Player 1 - Input Name (A-N, O-Z, backspace, end)
        6 characters max
        Fewer characters will try and center the Input, leaning left on a rounding fraction
    Would you like a new character ?(yes, no)
        Yes - changes the player character/sprite
            - 8 models, each loop changes the pallet
        No - Confirms player selection
            1 Human Player
                Fill remaining 2 Podiums with random selection
            2 Human Player 
